{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "xkpzxse5sea",
    "category": "story",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XkPZXSe5seA",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "MINE",
      "zh": "我的",
      "ja": "私の",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My!",
      "zh": "我的！",
      "ja": "私の！",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Breakfast Delivery for Emma.",
      "zh": "早餐送來給艾瑪。",
      "ja": "エマへの朝食の配達です。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh!",
      "zh": "哦！",
      "ja": "ああ！",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe they gave us a bonus burger today.",
      "zh": "也許今天多給了我們一個漢堡。",
      "ja": "今日はボーナスバーガーをくれたかも。",
      "time": "00:01:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This giant one is perfect for David.",
      "zh": "這個巨大的漢堡很適合大衛。",
      "ja": "この巨大なやつはデイビッドにぴったりだ。",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Breakfast! Everyone, come down!",
      "zh": "早餐好了！大家下來！",
      "ja": "朝ごはんだ！みんな降りてきて！",
      "time": "00:01:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm hungry. You are always hungry.",
      "zh": "我餓了。你總是餓。",
      "ja": "お腹すいた。君はいつもお腹すいてるね。",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait. Why do I not have a burger?",
      "zh": "等等。為什麼我沒有漢堡？",
      "ja": "待って。なんで僕のバーガーがないの？",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What? I put one there.",
      "zh": "什麼？我放了一個在那裡。",
      "ja": "え？そこに置いたよ。",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, really. I put the big one right there.",
      "zh": "真的，我把大的放在那裡。",
      "ja": "本当に。大きいのをそこに置いたんだ。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe Dad ate it in his sleep.",
      "zh": "也許爸爸睡著時吃了它。",
      "ja": "パパが寝てる間に食べちゃったのかも。",
      "time": "00:02:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Very funny.",
      "zh": "真有趣。",
      "ja": "面白いね。",
      "time": "00:02:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why is my burger over there?",
      "zh": "為什麼我的漢堡在那裡？",
      "ja": "なんで僕のバーガーがあそこにあるの？",
      "time": "00:02:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh? What is...",
      "zh": "咦？那是什麼...",
      "ja": "え？何だこれ...",
      "time": "00:02:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah!",
      "zh": "啊！",
      "ja": "あっ！",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What's that? Is that a turtle?",
      "zh": "那是什麼？是隻烏龜嗎？",
      "ja": "あれは何？カメ？",
      "time": "00:02:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why is there a turtle in my burger?",
      "zh": "為什麼我的漢堡裡有隻烏龜？",
      "ja": "なんで僕のバーガーにカメがいるの？",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's a baby turtle.",
      "zh": "這是一隻小烏龜。",
      "ja": "赤ちゃんカメだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait. Let me help him.",
      "zh": "等等。讓我幫幫他。",
      "ja": "待って。助けてあげる。",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's okay.",
      "zh": "他沒事。",
      "ja": "大丈夫だよ。",
      "time": "00:02:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's so tiny. He really came out of the burger.",
      "zh": "他好小。他真的從漢堡裡出來了。",
      "ja": "すごく小さい。ほんとにバーガーから出てきたんだ。",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is not a regular turtle.",
      "zh": "這不是普通的烏龜。",
      "ja": "これは普通のカメじゃない。",
      "time": "00:03:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think this is a baby sea turtle.",
      "zh": "我想這是一隻海龜寶寶。",
      "ja": "これは赤ちゃんウミガメだと思う。",
      "time": "00:03:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A sea turtle from the sea?",
      "zh": "海裡來的海龜？",
      "ja": "海から来たウミガメ？",
      "time": "00:03:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Definitely not from my breakfast.",
      "zh": "絕對不是從我的早餐來的。",
      "ja": "絶対に僕の朝食からじゃないよ。",
      "time": "00:03:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom, Dad. Can we keep him?",
      "zh": "媽媽，爸爸。我們可以養他嗎？",
      "ja": "ママ、パパ。飼ってもいい？",
      "time": "00:03:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Peter. Please.",
      "zh": "彼得，拜託。",
      "ja": "ピーター、お願い。",
      "time": "00:03:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He came to our house. He chose us.",
      "zh": "他來到我們家。他選擇了我們。",
      "ja": "彼はうちに来たんだ。僕たちを選んだんだよ。",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think he fell into a burger.",
      "zh": "我想他掉進漢堡裡了。",
      "ja": "多分バーガーに落ちちゃったんだ。",
      "time": "00:03:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Still, please.",
      "zh": "還是，拜託。",
      "ja": "それでもお願い。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Baby sea turtles hatch from eggs on sandy beaches.",
      "zh": "海龜寶寶是從沙灘上的蛋孵化出來的。",
      "ja": "ウミガメの赤ちゃんは砂浜の卵から孵るんだよ。",
      "time": "00:03:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So he was supposed to go to the ocean?",
      "zh": "所以他本該去海洋？",
      "ja": "だから海に行くはずだったの？",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "そうだよ。",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sea turtles belong in the ocean.",
      "zh": "海龜應該待在海裡。",
      "ja": "ウミガメは海にいるべきなんだ。",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:03:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We cannot keep a wild sea turtle forever.",
      "zh": "我們不能永遠養一隻野生海龜。",
      "ja": "野生のウミガメをずっと飼うことはできないよ。",
      "time": "00:03:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I know. Just for now.",
      "zh": "我知道。只是暫時。",
      "ja": "わかってる。今だけだよ。",
      "time": "00:03:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We can help him.",
      "zh": "我們可以幫助他。",
      "ja": "助けてあげられるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He needs the right space.",
      "zh": "他需要適合的空間。",
      "ja": "適切な場所が必要だ。",
      "time": "00:04:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sand, shallow water, and warmth.",
      "zh": "沙子、淺水和溫暖。",
      "ja": "砂、浅い水、そして暖かさ。",
      "time": "00:04:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We can buy everything.",
      "zh": "我們可以買齊所有東西。",
      "ja": "全部買えるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "いいよ。",
      "time": "00:04:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "いいよ。",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This afternoon, I'll take you and Anna to buy what he needs.",
      "zh": "今天下午，我會帶你和安娜去買他需要的東西。",
      "ja": "今日の午後、君とアンナを連れて必要なものを買いに行くよ。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes!",
      "zh": "好！",
      "ja": "やった！",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Temporary only.",
      "zh": "只是暫時的。",
      "ja": "一時的なものだよ。",
      "time": "00:04:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Temporary turtle rescue?",
      "zh": "暫時的烏龜救援？",
      "ja": "一時的なカメのレスキュー？",
      "time": "00:04:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That sounds official.",
      "zh": "聽起來很正式。",
      "ja": "それは正式に聞こえるね。",
      "time": "00:04:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He needs a name.",
      "zh": "他需要一個名字。",
      "ja": "名前が必要だね。",
      "time": "00:04:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe Shelley.",
      "zh": "也許叫Shelley。",
      "ja": "シェリーはどう？",
      "time": "00:04:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Too obvious.",
      "zh": "太明顯了。",
      "ja": "それはあからさますぎる。",
      "time": "00:04:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Burger.",
      "zh": "漢堡。",
      "ja": "バーガー。",
      "time": "00:04:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:04:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He came in a burger.",
      "zh": "他是從漢堡裡來的。",
      "ja": "バーガーの中から来たんだ。",
      "time": "00:04:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donnie.",
      "zh": "唐尼。",
      "ja": "ドニー。",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "See? He likes it.",
      "zh": "看？他喜歡這個。",
      "ja": "ほら？気に入ったみたい。",
      "time": "00:04:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Or he heard your voice.",
      "zh": "或者他聽到你的聲音。",
      "ja": "それか君の声を聞いたのかも。",
      "time": "00:04:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He likes it.",
      "zh": "他喜歡。",
      "ja": "気に入ったよ。",
      "time": "00:04:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "His name is Donnie.",
      "zh": "他的名字是唐尼。",
      "ja": "名前はドニーだ。",
      "time": "00:04:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donnie needs a bed.",
      "zh": "唐尼需要一張床。",
      "ja": "ドニーにはベッドが必要だ。",
      "time": "00:04:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A turtle bed?",
      "zh": "烏龜床？",
      "ja": "カメのベッド？",
      "time": "00:05:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "そう。",
      "time": "00:05:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And maybe sunglasses.",
      "zh": "也許還要太陽眼鏡。",
      "ja": "それとサングラスも。",
      "time": "00:05:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Turtles do not wear sunglasses.",
      "zh": "烏龜不戴太陽眼鏡。",
      "ja": "カメはサングラスをかけないよ。",
      "time": "00:05:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Cool turtles do.",
      "zh": "酷烏龜會戴。",
      "ja": "かっこいいカメはかけるよ。",
      "time": "00:05:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We are buying the basics.",
      "zh": "我們買基本的東西。",
      "ja": "基本的なものを買うんだ。",
      "time": "00:05:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe a tiny jacket?",
      "zh": "也許一件小外套？",
      "ja": "小さなジャケットも？",
      "time": "00:05:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How do you know Donnie is a boy?",
      "zh": "你怎麼知道唐尼是男生？",
      "ja": "どうしてドニーが男の子だとわかるの？",
      "time": "00:05:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Because his name is Donnie.",
      "zh": "因為他的名字是唐尼。",
      "ja": "名前がドニーだから。",
      "time": "00:05:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That is not science.",
      "zh": "那不是科學。",
      "ja": "それは科学じゃないよ。",
      "time": "00:05:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Then Donnie can still be Donnie.",
      "zh": "那唐尼還是可以叫唐尼。",
      "ja": "じゃあドニーのままでいいよ。",
      "time": "00:05:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Problem solved.",
      "zh": "問題解決。",
      "ja": "問題解決だね。",
      "time": "00:05:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi there.",
      "zh": "嗨。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Can I help you?",
      "zh": "我能幫你嗎？",
      "ja": "何かお手伝いしましょうか？",
      "time": "00:05:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We have a baby sea turtle.",
      "zh": "我們有一隻海龜寶寶。",
      "ja": "赤ちゃんウミガメがいるんです。",
      "time": "00:05:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You have a what?",
      "zh": "你說你有什麼？",
      "ja": "何を持ってるって？",
      "time": "00:05:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:05:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Then let's get the right temporary supplies.",
      "zh": "那我們去買合適的臨時用品吧。",
      "ja": "じゃあ適切な一時的用品を揃えましょう。",
      "time": "00:05:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can Donnie have that?",
      "zh": "唐尼可以用那個嗎？",
      "ja": "ドニーはそれを使える？",
      "time": "00:05:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不行。",
      "ja": "ダメです。",
      "time": "00:05:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe Donnie wants this.",
      "zh": "也許唐尼想要這個。",
      "ja": "ドニーはこれが欲しいかも。",
      "time": "00:05:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No. He needs a cool boy hat.",
      "zh": "不，他需要一頂酷酷的男孩帽。",
      "ja": "ダメ。かっこいい男の子の帽子が必要だ。",
      "time": "00:06:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You do not even know if Donnie is a boy.",
      "zh": "你甚至不知道唐尼是不是男孩。",
      "ja": "ドニーが男の子かどうかもわからないのに。",
      "time": "00:06:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You do not know if Donnie is a girl.",
      "zh": "你也不知道唐尼是不是女孩。",
      "ja": "ドニーが女の子かもしれないよ。",
      "time": "00:06:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "When sea turtles are babies, it's hard to tell.",
      "zh": "海龜寶寶時很難分辨。",
      "ja": "ウミガメの赤ちゃんは性別がわかりにくいんだ。",
      "time": "00:06:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So Donnie is just Donnie.",
      "zh": "所以唐尼就是唐尼。",
      "ja": "だからドニーはドニーだよ。",
      "time": "00:06:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That is acceptable.",
      "zh": "這樣可以接受。",
      "ja": "それでいいよ。",
      "time": "00:06:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He needs a simple safe place for now.",
      "zh": "他現在需要一個簡單安全的地方。",
      "ja": "今はシンプルで安全な場所が必要だ。",
      "time": "00:06:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And later he needs to go back where he belongs.",
      "zh": "之後他需要回到他該去的地方。",
      "ja": "そして後で彼は元の場所に戻らなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:06:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The ocean.",
      "zh": "海洋。",
      "ja": "海だ。",
      "time": "00:06:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "zh": "沒錯。",
      "ja": "その通り。",
      "time": "00:06:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We are helping him.",
      "zh": "我們在幫助他。",
      "ja": "僕たちは彼を助けているんだ。",
      "time": "00:06:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That actually looks pretty good.",
      "zh": "看起來真的不錯。",
      "ja": "実際かなりいい感じだね。",
      "time": "00:06:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Welcome home, Donnie.",
      "zh": "歡迎回家，唐尼。",
      "ja": "お帰り、ドニー。",
      "time": "00:06:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He likes it.",
      "zh": "他喜歡。",
      "ja": "気に入ったみたい。",
      "time": "00:06:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He is inspecting it.",
      "zh": "他正在檢查它。",
      "ja": "チェックしてるよ。",
      "time": "00:06:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:06:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I hope the customer is satisfied.",
      "zh": "希望顧客滿意。",
      "ja": "お客さんが満足してくれるといいな。",
      "time": "00:06:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good night, Donnie.",
      "zh": "晚安，唐尼。",
      "ja": "おやすみ、ドニー。",
      "time": "00:07:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good night, burger turtle.",
      "zh": "晚安，漢堡烏龜。",
      "ja": "おやすみ、バーガーカメ。",
      "time": "00:07:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He is not burger turtle.",
      "zh": "他不是漢堡烏龜。",
      "ja": "彼はバーガーカメじゃないよ。",
      "time": "00:07:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He was literally in a burger.",
      "zh": "他真的在漢堡裡。",
      "ja": "本当にバーガーの中にいたんだ。",
      "time": "00:07:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He waved.",
      "zh": "他揮手了。",
      "ja": "手を振ったよ。",
      "time": "00:07:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sleep well, Donnie.",
      "zh": "睡個好覺，唐尼。",
      "ja": "よく眠ってね、ドニー。",
      "time": "00:07:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine.",
      "zh": "我的。",
      "ja": "僕の。",
      "time": "00:07:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bye, Donnie.",
      "zh": "再見，唐尼。",
      "ja": "バイバイ、ドニー。",
      "time": "00:07:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Be good today.",
      "zh": "今天乖乖的。",
      "ja": "今日はいい子でね。",
      "time": "00:07:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll be back after school.",
      "zh": "放學後我會回來。",
      "ja": "学校の後で戻ってくるよ。",
      "time": "00:07:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He is a turtle, Peter.",
      "zh": "他是隻烏龜，彼得。",
      "ja": "彼はカメだよ、ピーター。",
      "time": "00:07:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He is not going anywhere.",
      "zh": "他不會去哪裡。",
      "ja": "どこにも行かないよ。",
      "time": "00:07:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You do not know that.",
      "zh": "你不知道。",
      "ja": "それはわからないよ。",
      "time": "00:07:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Time to go.",
      "zh": "該走了。",
      "ja": "行く時間だ。",
      "time": "00:07:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No escaping.",
      "zh": "不准逃跑。",
      "ja": "逃げちゃダメ。",
      "time": "00:07:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No parties.",
      "zh": "不准開派對。",
      "ja": "パーティー禁止。",
      "time": "00:07:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No burger stealing.",
      "zh": "不准偷漢堡。",
      "ja": "バーガーを盗むな。",
      "time": "00:07:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Come on, Captain Peter.",
      "zh": "來吧，彼得隊長。",
      "ja": "さあ、キャプテンピーター。",
      "time": "00:07:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine.",
      "zh": "我的。",
      "ja": "僕の。",
      "time": "00:08:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait.",
      "zh": "等等。",
      "ja": "待って。",
      "time": "00:08:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine.",
      "zh": "我的。",
      "ja": "僕の。",
      "time": "00:08:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ninjatural.",
      "zh": "忍者自然。",
      "ja": "忍者ナチュラル。",
      "time": "00:08:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And Captain Hook.",
      "zh": "還有虎克船長。",
      "ja": "そしてキャプテンフック。",
      "time": "00:08:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine.",
      "zh": "我的。",
      "ja": "僕の。",
      "time": "00:08:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donnie, I'm home.",
      "zh": "唐尼，我回來了。",
      "ja": "ドニー、ただいま。",
      "time": "00:09:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donnie?",
      "zh": "唐尼？",
      "ja": "ドニー？",
      "time": "00:09:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donnie?",
      "zh": "唐尼？",
      "ja": "ドニー？",
      "time": "00:09:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe he is hiding.",
      "zh": "也許他在躲藏。",
      "ja": "隠れてるのかも。",
      "time": "00:09:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Turtles do not hide that fast.",
      "zh": "烏龜不會躲那麼快。",
      "ja": "カメはそんなに早く隠れないよ。",
      "time": "00:09:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donnie!",
      "zh": "唐尼！",
      "ja": "ドニー！",
      "time": "00:09:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donnie!",
      "zh": "唐尼！",
      "ja": "ドニー！",
      "time": "00:09:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What's wrong?",
      "zh": "怎麼了？",
      "ja": "どうしたの？",
      "time": "00:09:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donnie is gone.",
      "zh": "唐尼不見了。",
      "ja": "ドニーがいない。",
      "time": "00:09:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What happened?",
      "zh": "發生什麼事？",
      "ja": "何があったの？",
      "time": "00:09:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's missing.",
      "zh": "他失蹤了。",
      "ja": "行方不明だ。",
      "time": "00:09:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That was not here before.",
      "zh": "那個之前不在這裡。",
      "ja": "これは前はなかった。",
      "time": "00:09:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A bird?",
      "zh": "一隻鳥？",
      "ja": "鳥？",
      "time": "00:09:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A bird took Donnie?",
      "zh": "有鳥帶走唐尼？",
      "ja": "鳥がドニーを連れて行ったの？",
      "time": "00:09:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We do not know yet.",
      "zh": "我們還不知道。",
      "ja": "まだわからない。",
      "time": "00:09:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But we will look for him.",
      "zh": "但我們會找他。",
      "ja": "でも探すよ。",
      "time": "00:09:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I should have stayed home.",
      "zh": "我本該待在家。",
      "ja": "家にいるべきだった。",
      "time": "00:09:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不。",
      "ja": "違うよ。",
      "time": "00:09:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is not your fault.",
      "zh": "這不是你的錯。",
      "ja": "君のせいじゃない。",
      "time": "00:09:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We will find him.",
      "zh": "我們會找到他的。",
      "ja": "見つけるよ。",
      "time": "00:09:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donnie!",
      "zh": "唐尼！",
      "ja": "ドニー！",
      "time": "00:09:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donnie!",
      "zh": "唐尼！",
      "ja": "ドニー！",
      "time": "00:10:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donnie!",
      "zh": "唐尼！",
      "ja": "ドニー！",
      "time": "00:10:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did you see anything strange?",
      "zh": "你有看到什麼奇怪的嗎？",
      "ja": "変なもの見なかった？",
      "time": "00:10:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I made space on my shelf.",
      "zh": "我在書架上騰出空間了。",
      "ja": "棚にスペースを作ったよ。",
      "time": "00:10:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If Donnie comes back, he can sit there.",
      "zh": "如果唐尼回來，他可以坐那裡。",
      "ja": "ドニーが戻ったらそこに座れるよ。",
      "time": "00:10:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Really?",
      "zh": "真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本当に？",
      "time": "00:10:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:10:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But only if he does not steal my pencils.",
      "zh": "但前提是他不偷我的鉛筆。",
      "ja": "でも鉛筆を盗まなければね。",
      "time": "00:10:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We will keep looking tomorrow.",
      "zh": "我們明天繼續找。",
      "ja": "明日も探すよ。",
      "time": "00:10:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What if he is scared?",
      "zh": "如果他害怕呢？",
      "ja": "もし怖がってたら？",
      "time": "00:10:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Then we find him faster.",
      "zh": "那我們會更快找到他。",
      "ja": "そうしたらもっと早く見つけられる。",
      "time": "00:10:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And if any bird took him, that bird picked the wrong family.",
      "zh": "如果有鳥帶走他，那隻鳥選錯家庭了。",
      "ja": "もし鳥が連れて行ったなら、その鳥は間違った家族を選んだんだ。",
      "time": "00:10:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine.",
      "zh": "我的。",
      "ja": "僕の。",
      "time": "00:11:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine.",
      "zh": "我的。",
      "ja": "僕の。",
      "time": "00:11:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Gold and jellyfish.",
      "zh": "金色和水母。",
      "ja": "ゴールドとクラゲ。",
      "time": "00:11:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's fine.",
      "zh": "那沒關係。",
      "ja": "それでいいよ。",
      "time": "00:11:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But not the other one.",
      "zh": "但不是另一個。",
      "ja": "でももう一つはダメ。",
      "time": "00:11:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They are.",
      "zh": "它們是。",
      "ja": "そうだよ。",
      "time": "00:12:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come on!",
      "zh": "來吧！",
      "ja": "さあ！",
      "time": "00:12:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey!",
      "zh": "嘿！",
      "ja": "おい！",
      "time": "00:12:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No way!",
      "zh": "不可能！",
      "ja": "ありえない！",
      "time": "00:12:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come on!",
      "zh": "來吧！",
      "ja": "さあ！",
      "time": "00:12:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine!",
      "zh": "我的！",
      "ja": "僕の！",
      "time": "00:13:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Eat a little first.",
      "zh": "先吃一點。",
      "ja": "ちょっと食べて。",
      "time": "00:13:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm not hungry.",
      "zh": "我不餓。",
      "ja": "お腹すいてない。",
      "time": "00:13:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That is how I know you are truly sad.",
      "zh": "我知道你真的很難過。",
      "ja": "それで君が本当に悲しいってわかるんだ。",
      "time": "00:13:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait!",
      "zh": "等等！",
      "ja": "待って！",
      "time": "00:13:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donny!",
      "zh": "唐尼！",
      "ja": "ドニー！",
      "time": "00:13:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's really him!",
      "zh": "真的是他！",
      "ja": "本当に彼だ！",
      "time": "00:13:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donny!",
      "zh": "唐尼！",
      "ja": "ドニー！",
      "time": "00:13:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sandals first.",
      "zh": "先穿涼鞋。",
      "ja": "まずサンダルを履こう。",
      "time": "00:13:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's go!",
      "zh": "走吧！",
      "ja": "行こう！",
      "time": "00:13:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donny!",
      "zh": "唐尼！",
      "ja": "ドニー！",
      "time": "00:13:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine, mine!",
      "zh": "我的，我的！",
      "ja": "僕の、僕の！",
      "time": "00:13:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There they are!",
      "zh": "他們在那裡！",
      "ja": "あそこにいる！",
      "time": "00:13:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no!",
      "zh": "糟了！",
      "ja": "やばい！",
      "time": "00:13:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine, mine, mine!",
      "zh": "我的，我的，我的！",
      "ja": "僕の、僕の、僕の！",
      "time": "00:13:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donny, wait!",
      "zh": "唐尼，等等！",
      "ja": "ドニー、待って！",
      "time": "00:13:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Peter!",
      "zh": "彼得！",
      "ja": "ピーター！",
      "time": "00:13:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This way!",
      "zh": "這邊！",
      "ja": "こっち！",
      "time": "00:13:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Easy.",
      "zh": "輕鬆點。",
      "ja": "落ち着いて。",
      "time": "00:14:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's my turtle!",
      "zh": "那是我的烏龜！",
      "ja": "あれは僕のカメだ！",
      "time": "00:14:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That is not your turtle.",
      "zh": "那不是你的烏龜。",
      "ja": "それは君のカメじゃないよ。",
      "time": "00:14:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donny!",
      "zh": "唐尼！",
      "ja": "ドニー！",
      "time": "00:14:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donny!",
      "zh": "唐尼！",
      "ja": "ドニー！",
      "time": "00:14:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's skateboarding!",
      "zh": "他在滑滑板！",
      "ja": "スケートボードに乗ってる！",
      "time": "00:14:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Got you.",
      "zh": "抓到了。",
      "ja": "捕まえた。",
      "time": "00:14:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donny!",
      "zh": "唐尼！",
      "ja": "ドニー！",
      "time": "00:14:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're okay.",
      "zh": "你沒事吧。",
      "ja": "大丈夫だね。",
      "time": "00:14:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My brother!",
      "zh": "我的兄弟！",
      "ja": "僕の兄弟！",
      "time": "00:14:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Leave him alone!",
      "zh": "別碰他！",
      "ja": "ほっといて！",
      "time": "00:14:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's mine!",
      "zh": "他是我的！",
      "ja": "彼は僕のだ！",
      "time": "00:14:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He is literally saying mine, not yours.",
      "zh": "他真的在說我的，不是你的。",
      "ja": "彼は文字通り「僕の」って言ってるんだよ、「君の」じゃなくて。",
      "time": "00:14:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let the bird go.",
      "zh": "放開那隻鳥。",
      "ja": "鳥を離して。",
      "time": "00:14:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No!",
      "zh": "不！",
      "ja": "ダメ！",
      "time": "00:14:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's okay.",
      "zh": "他沒事。",
      "ja": "彼は大丈夫だよ。",
      "time": "00:15:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine, mine, mine!",
      "zh": "我的，我的，我的！",
      "ja": "僕の、僕の、僕の！",
      "time": "00:15:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine, mine, mine!",
      "zh": "我的，我的，我的！",
      "ja": "僕の、僕の、僕の！",
      "time": "00:15:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, stop!",
      "zh": "嘿，停下！",
      "ja": "おい、やめて！",
      "time": "00:15:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine, mine, mine!",
      "zh": "我的，我的，我的！",
      "ja": "僕の、僕の、僕の！",
      "time": "00:15:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He actually called his friends.",
      "zh": "他真的叫了他的朋友們。",
      "ja": "彼は本当に友達を呼んだんだ。",
      "time": "00:15:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You saved us.",
      "zh": "你救了我們。",
      "ja": "君は僕たちを救った。",
      "time": "00:15:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine.",
      "zh": "我的。",
      "ja": "僕の。",
      "time": "00:15:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think he wants to come with us.",
      "zh": "我覺得他想跟我們一起走。",
      "ja": "彼は僕たちと一緒に行きたいみたい。",
      "time": "00:15:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "One ride only, no stealing.",
      "zh": "只能搭一次車，不准偷東西。",
      "ja": "一回だけ乗せて、盗みはダメ。",
      "time": "00:15:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Everyone buckled?",
      "zh": "大家都繫好安全帶了嗎？",
      "ja": "みんなシートベルト締めた？",
      "time": "00:15:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The bird is not buckled.",
      "zh": "那隻鳥沒繫安全帶。",
      "ja": "鳥はシートベルトしてない。",
      "time": "00:15:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine.",
      "zh": "我的。",
      "ja": "僕の。",
      "time": "00:15:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We're taking you home now.",
      "zh": "我們現在帶你回家。",
      "ja": "今から君を家に連れて行くよ。",
      "time": "00:16:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "For real this time.",
      "zh": "這次是真的。",
      "ja": "今度こそ本当だ。",
      "time": "00:16:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's what love does.",
      "zh": "這就是愛的表現。",
      "ja": "それが愛ってものだ。",
      "time": "00:16:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It helps, even when saying goodbye is hard.",
      "zh": "即使說再見很難，它仍然會幫助。",
      "ja": "さよならを言うのが辛くても、助けになるんだ。",
      "time": "00:16:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is where he belongs.",
      "zh": "這是他該去的地方。",
      "ja": "ここが彼の居場所だ。",
      "time": "00:16:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I know.",
      "zh": "我知道。",
      "ja": "わかってる。",
      "time": "00:16:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bye, Donny.",
      "zh": "再見，唐尼。",
      "ja": "バイバイ、ドニー。",
      "time": "00:16:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm going to miss you.",
      "zh": "我會想你的。",
      "ja": "寂しくなるよ。",
      "time": "00:16:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He will be okay.",
      "zh": "他會沒事的。",
      "ja": "彼は大丈夫だよ。",
      "time": "00:16:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He made it this far.",
      "zh": "他已經走到這裡了。",
      "ja": "ここまで来たんだ。",
      "time": "00:16:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And now he gets to go home.",
      "zh": "現在他可以回家了。",
      "ja": "そして今、家に帰れる。",
      "time": "00:16:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "His family, they came for him.",
      "zh": "他的家人來接他了。",
      "ja": "家族が迎えに来たんだ。",
      "time": "00:17:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bye, Donny.",
      "zh": "再見，唐尼。",
      "ja": "バイバイ、ドニー。",
      "time": "00:17:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you crying?",
      "zh": "你在哭嗎？",
      "ja": "泣いてるの？",
      "time": "00:17:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "沒有。",
      "ja": "違うよ。",
      "time": "00:17:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The ocean is just very windy.",
      "zh": "只是海邊風很大。",
      "ja": "海がただすごく風が強いだけ。",
      "time": "00:17:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Very windy.",
      "zh": "風很大。",
      "ja": "すごく風が強い。",
      "time": "00:17:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You helped him when he needed help.",
      "zh": "你在他需要幫助時幫了他。",
      "ja": "彼が助けを必要とした時に助けてあげた。",
      "time": "00:17:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That is something to be proud of.",
      "zh": "這是值得驕傲的事。",
      "ja": "それは誇りに思っていいことだよ。",
      "time": "00:17:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sea turtles belong in the ocean.",
      "zh": "海龜應該待在海裡。",
      "ja": "ウミガメは海にいるべきだ。",
      "time": "00:17:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "zh": "沒錯。",
      "ja": "その通り。",
      "time": "00:17:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think that means goodbye.",
      "zh": "我想這代表再見了。",
      "ja": "それはさよならの意味だと思う。",
      "time": "00:17:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now I have a question for you.",
      "zh": "現在我有個問題要問你。",
      "ja": "さて、質問があるよ。",
      "time": "00:17:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What does the seagull say?",
      "zh": "海鷗說什麼？",
      "ja": "カモメは何て言う？",
      "time": "00:17:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I know.",
      "zh": "我知道。",
      "ja": "わかるよ。",
      "time": "00:17:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wait.",
      "zh": "等等。",
      "ja": "待って。",
      "time": "00:17:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let them answer first.",
      "zh": "讓他們先回答。",
      "ja": "みんなに先に答えさせよう。",
      "time": "00:17:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "If you know the answer, please write it in the comments.",
      "zh": "如果你知道答案，請在留言寫下來。",
      "ja": "答えがわかったらコメントに書いてね。",
      "time": "00:17:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just write the words the seagull says.",
      "zh": "只要寫海鷗說的話。",
      "ja": "カモメの言葉だけを書いてね。",
      "time": "00:17:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:18:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Write it in the comments if you got it before me.",
      "zh": "如果你比我先知道，請寫在留言。",
      "ja": "もし僕より先にわかったらコメントに書いてね。",
      "time": "00:18:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See you next time.",
      "zh": "下次見。",
      "ja": "また次回。",
      "time": "00:18:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See you next time.",
      "zh": "下次見。",
      "ja": "また次回。",
      "time": "00:18:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See you next time.",
      "zh": "下次見。",
      "ja": "また次回。",
      "time": "00:18:32"
    }
  ]
}